# Cloud Build ignore – controls what gets uploaded to Cloud Build.
# We intentionally do NOT use #!include:.dockerignore because the .dockerignore
# pattern of "exclude apps/ then re-include !apps/shared/" is not reliably
# honored by gcloud's upload filter. Instead we replicate the relevant excludes
# here with targeted apps/* excludes that spare apps/shared/.

.git
.worktrees
.env
.env.*
.bun-cache
.bun
.tmp
**/.tmp
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.webp
*.gif
*.mp4
*.mov
*.wav
*.mp3
node_modules
**/node_modules
.pnpm-store
**/.pnpm-store
.turbo
**/.turbo
.cache
**/.cache
.next
**/.next
coverage
**/coverage
*.log
tmp
**/tmp

# build artifacts
dist
**/dist
apps/macos/.build
apps/ios/build
**/*.trace

# Large app trees — exclude specific subdirs instead of blanket apps/
apps/android/
apps/ios/
apps/macos/
assets/
Peekaboo/
Swabble/
Core/
Users/

# Include the lockfile (gitignored but required for Docker build)
!pnpm-lock.yaml
